1
00:00:04,393 --> 00:00:05,646
Avançar, Haemus—

2
00:00:09,825 --> 00:00:10,968
Não entre em pânico, Lumi!

3
00:00:11,100 --> 00:00:12,128
Lembra do treinamento?

4
00:00:12,948 --> 00:00:13,950
Estou bem aqui.

5
00:00:14,525 --> 00:00:15,300
Preparar...

6
00:00:16,025 --> 00:00:16,780
Agora!

7
00:00:16,850 --> 00:00:17,607
Pule!

8
00:00:19,103 --> 00:00:19,728
Atacar!

9
00:00:21,325 --> 00:00:22,400
Pare ela!

10
00:00:44,923 --> 00:00:45,648
Cuidado!

11
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:51,533
Essa é a vontade do destino...

12
00:00:52,910 --> 00:00:54,600
Estava terminado antes mesmo de começar.

13
00:01:01,010 --> 00:01:01,585
Lumi!

14
00:01:01,950 --> 00:01:02,750
Lumi...

15
00:01:06,675 --> 00:01:07,075
Oh!

16
00:01:13,638 --> 00:01:14,800
Você quer vir comigo?

17
00:01:15,875 --> 00:01:16,925
Então vamos!

18
00:01:17,485 --> 00:01:19,322
O mundo inteiro aguarda!

19
00:01:23,650 --> 00:01:24,800
Rawrrrr!

20
00:01:30,723 --> 00:01:33,775
Ya-hoo!!!

21
00:01:39,553 --> 00:01:40,278
Mas o quê...

22
00:01:57,643 --> 00:01:59,036
Não se preocupe, Haemus.

23
00:01:59,253 --> 00:02:00,576
A vitória será nossa!

24
00:02:20,093 --> 00:02:21,068
A profecia...

